    "narratives": {
      "Problem": "The current agent experience is fragmented: AgentList shows only Cloister + specialists (no work agents), GodView shows work agents in a cinematic grid but lacks dense views, timeline history, and relationship topology. Detail view is a full-screen modal that loses context.",
      "Proposal": "Create a single AgentsPage with four view modes (Live Grid, Command Table, Timeline, Topology), a slide-out detail panel, unified agent type, Cloister banner, stats row, and right panel \u2014 all event-sourced via WebSocket with URL-addressable state and keyboard shortcuts."
    },
